{
  "video_id": "bEusrD8g-dM",
  "title": "Creative thinking - how to get out of the box and generate ideas: Giovanni Corazza at TEDxRoma",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 24415.0,
      "end_time": 27200.0,
      "text": "Sometimes, easy means difficult."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 27200.0,
      "end_time": 30520.0,
      "text": "Have you ever been assigned an easy task,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 30520.0,
      "end_time": 33400.0,
      "text": "which for you is actually very difficult to perform,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 33400.0,
      "end_time": 35680.0,
      "text": "and maybe for nobody else?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 35680.0,
      "end_time": 38600.0,
      "text": "That is when you experience frustration."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 38600.0,
      "end_time": 42160.0,
      "text": "I have experienced that when I started taking singing lessons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 42160.0,
      "end_time": 45440.0,
      "text": "and my teacher told me to breathe with my diaphragm."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 45440.0,
      "end_time": 50400.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s easy, it&#39;s our natural breath, but actually very difficult to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 50400.0,
      "end_time": 54120.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s a secret of the great singers."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 54120.0,
      "end_time": 56800.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s similar to what happens"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 56800.0,
      "end_time": 61360.0,
      "text": "when a boss comes into a meeting and tells you to think out of the box."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 61360.0,
      "end_time": 64280.0,
      "text": "Come on, give me your creative ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 64280.0,
      "end_time": 67250.0,
      "text": "Think out of the box. I want to hear that."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 67250.0,
      "end_time": 69160.0,
      "text": "I need innovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 69160.0,
      "end_time": 72400.0,
      "text": "Easy, simple, but actually very hard to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 72400.0,
      "end_time": 73920.0,
      "text": "You need to practice."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 73920.0,
      "end_time": 78480.0,
      "text": "You need to know how to get out of the box, where to go,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 78480.0,
      "end_time": 82240.0,
      "text": "and how to come back inside the box, because that&#39;s where we live."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 82240.0,
      "end_time": 84360.0,
      "text": "We actually live inside our boxes."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 84360.0,
      "end_time": 86660.0,
      "text": "I want to ask these questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 86660.0,
      "end_time": 88840.0,
      "text": "I asked those questions to myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 88840.0,
      "end_time": 92360.0,
      "text": "This presentation is a little journey through my answers."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 92360.0,
      "end_time": 95520.0,
      "text": "I hope that some of these will resonate with yours."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 95520.0,
      "end_time": 97920.0,
      "text": "The first thing is to ask, why."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 97920.0,
      "end_time": 100920.0,
      "text": "Why should you really go out of the box?"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 100920.0,
      "end_time": 103850.0,
      "text": "Because inside the box, we feel safe."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 103850.0,
      "end_time": 106920.0,
      "text": "We agree with everybody else."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 106920.0,
      "end_time": 110880.0,
      "text": "And when we go out, we risk our reputation."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 110880.0,
      "end_time": 114360.0,
      "text": "We worked so hard for a lifetime to build it up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 114360.0,
      "end_time": 116800.0,
      "text": "why should we risk it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 116800.0,
      "end_time": 121760.0,
      "text": "Is this something which is a luxury, that only a few people can do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 121760.0,
      "end_time": 123920.0,
      "text": "or is it really a necessity?"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 123920.0,
      "end_time": 125080.0,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 125080.0,
      "end_time": 127000.0,
      "text": "Think of our lives today."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 127000.0,
      "end_time": 129600.0,
      "text": "We are really a part of a network."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 129600.0,
      "end_time": 131760.0,
      "text": "We are nodes in a network."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 131760.0,
      "end_time": 134720.0,
      "text": "We share information in a real time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 134720.0,
      "end_time": 139640.0,
      "text": "and we, in the end, all possess the same information."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 139640.0,
      "end_time": 144200.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the end of it, and that is a scary thought."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 144200.0,
      "end_time": 147120.0,
      "text": "If we all possess the same information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 147120.0,
      "end_time": 150080.0,
      "text": "what makes a difference between ourselves?"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 150080.0,
      "end_time": 154800.0,
      "text": "Where does our dignity as human beings lie?"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 154800.0,
      "end_time": 161903.0,
      "text": "It really depends on what we generate with that common shared information."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 161903.0,
      "end_time": 166520.0,
      "text": "To think creatively, to go out of the box, is not a luxury."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 166520.0,
      "end_time": 171560.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a necessity for us, and for our dignity as human beings."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 171560.0,
      "end_time": 173840.0,
      "text": "Which box are we talking about?"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 173840.0,
      "end_time": 176240.0,
      "text": "We must have a clear definition,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 176240.0,
      "end_time": 179760.0,
      "text": "so that we are really talking about something specific."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 179760.0,
      "end_time": 183560.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not our mind; we cannot think out of our minds."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 183560.0,
      "end_time": 187280.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a boundary within our minds."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 187280.0,
      "end_time": 190000.0,
      "text": "The boundary between what we know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 190000.0,
      "end_time": 194560.0,
      "text": "and what we haven&#39;t still, or yet, thought about."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 194560.0,
      "end_time": 195840.0,
      "text": "What is our mind?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 195840.0,
      "end_time": 197560.0,
      "text": "What is our knowledge structure?"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 197560.0,
      "end_time": 201840.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an emergent phenomenon out of the complex mechanism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 201840.0,
      "end_time": 204210.0,
      "text": "which is the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 204210.0,
      "end_time": 208240.0,
      "text": "We start with initial conditions, our genetic heritage."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 208240.0,
      "end_time": 211964.0,
      "text": "We have boundary conditions, the environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 211964.0,
      "end_time": 214200.0,
      "text": "We have indirect experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 214200.0,
      "end_time": 217240.0,
      "text": "years and years spent in school and University"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 217240.0,
      "end_time": 219720.0,
      "text": "to learn what other people have thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 219720.0,
      "end_time": 221443.0,
      "text": "what other people have discovered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 221443.0,
      "end_time": 222920.0,
      "text": "what other people have created."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 222920.0,
      "end_time": 225760.0,
      "text": "Then, we have our own direct experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 225760.0,
      "end_time": 230160.0,
      "text": "our successes, our failures that really make what we are."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 230160.0,
      "end_time": 234920.0,
      "text": "All of this builds the anthill within which we live,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 234920.0,
      "end_time": 237440.0,
      "text": "and we live very well in that."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 237440.0,
      "end_time": 243360.0,
      "text": "Whatever we think inside that anthill, that box, we feel safe."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 243360.0,
      "end_time": 246000.0,
      "text": "Whatever is outside, it&#39;s invisible to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 246000.0,
      "end_time": 248400.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t know what it&#39;s outside."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 248400.0,
      "end_time": 254396.0,
      "text": "That is why it&#39;s so risky, because nobody else knows."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 254396.0,
      "end_time": 258464.0,
      "text": "We are faced with something which is necessary to our dignity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 258464.0,
      "end_time": 261561.0,
      "text": "but actually it&#39;s very difficult to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 261560.99999999997,
      "end_time": 264800.0,
      "text": "How do we go out of the box? How do we do that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 264800.0,
      "end_time": 266360.0,
      "text": "What are the mechanisms?"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 266360.0,
      "end_time": 270800.0,
      "text": "Do we need to wait for an apple to fall on our heads,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 270800.0,
      "end_time": 274040.0,
      "text": "or are there some specific techniques?"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 274040.0,
      "end_time": 277200.0,
      "text": "Reality is out there for us to perceive it."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 277200.0,
      "end_time": 280000.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s beautiful. You see these flowers."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 280000.0,
      "end_time": 284960.0,
      "text": "We have a lot of ideas, which is our convergent information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 284960.0,
      "end_time": 286680.0,
      "text": "the dominant ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 286680.0,
      "end_time": 290720.0,
      "text": "Whenever we need to think about an area, a focused area,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 290720.0,
      "end_time": 293560.0,
      "text": "we have ideas on how things should be."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 293560.0,
      "end_time": 296840.0,
      "text": "We have requirements, we have specifications."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 296840.0,
      "end_time": 298960.0,
      "text": "We know how things are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 298960.0,
      "end_time": 302560.0,
      "text": "because that&#39;s the way they always have been."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 302560.0,
      "end_time": 304320.0,
      "text": "But if we want to go out of the box,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 304320.0,
      "end_time": 308040.0,
      "text": "we need to add something more, a little spice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 308040.0,
      "end_time": 311920.0,
      "text": "something which goes beyond the convergent information."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 311920.0,
      "end_time": 315400.0,
      "text": "Something wrong, something absurd,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 315400.0,
      "end_time": 318320.0,
      "text": "something which apparently is not relevant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 318320.0,
      "end_time": 320920.0,
      "text": "something which takes us far."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 320920.0,
      "end_time": 324280.0,
      "text": "This is what we call divergent information."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 324280.0,
      "end_time": 328000.0,
      "text": "We need a little bit of that divergent information"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 328000.0,
      "end_time": 331280.0,
      "text": "to cross the borders within our minds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 331280.0,
      "end_time": 335320.0,
      "text": "from what we know to what we haven&#39;t yet thought about."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 335320.0,
      "end_time": 340440.0,
      "text": "This is the essential mechanism that is necessary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 340440.0,
      "end_time": 345440.0,
      "text": "and it takes us to a place where we don&#39;t really know where to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 345440.0,
      "end_time": 347120.0,
      "text": "We are suspended."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 347120.0,
      "end_time": 349760.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s like the middle game in chess."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 349760.0,
      "end_time": 352440.0,
      "text": "Where do you go once you&#39;re out of the box?"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 352440.0,
      "end_time": 355880.0,
      "text": "You have no preset direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 355880.0,
      "end_time": 359710.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s really a potential situation"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 359710.0,
      "end_time": 364720.0,
      "text": "that brings us to a feeling that we should immediately go back."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 364720.0,
      "end_time": 366400.0,
      "text": "This does not make any sense."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 366400.0,
      "end_time": 370760.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s go back to safe place. Let&#39;s go back inside the box."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 370760.0,
      "end_time": 375433.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a temptation that we need to resist."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 375433.0,
      "end_time": 378920.0,
      "text": "We need to value long thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 378920.0,
      "end_time": 381840.0,
      "text": "Normally, we talk about brilliant thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 381840.0,
      "end_time": 384600.0,
      "text": "fast thinking, deep thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 384600.0,
      "end_time": 387020.0,
      "text": "but here we&#39;re talking about something different,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 387020.0,
      "end_time": 388800.0,
      "text": "long thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 388800.0,
      "end_time": 390240.0,
      "text": "What does that mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 390240.0,
      "end_time": 394000.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s some thought that takes us far."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 394000.0,
      "end_time": 397680.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s as if you were reading poetry or listening to music."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 397680.0,
      "end_time": 400740.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t judge the single notes."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 400740.0,
      "end_time": 403200.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t judge the single words."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 403200.0,
      "end_time": 408000.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the ensemble that gives you a feeling, and takes you far."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 408000.0,
      "end_time": 411760.0,
      "text": "We must do the same thing with our concepts."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 411760.0,
      "end_time": 414200.0,
      "text": "We need to go far."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 414200.0,
      "end_time": 417360.0,
      "text": "We can use association of ideas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 417360.0,
      "end_time": 421320.0,
      "text": "combination of ideas, extraction of principles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 421320.0,
      "end_time": 423520.0,
      "text": "and application of those principles"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 423520.0,
      "end_time": 426560.0,
      "text": "to areas where they were never applied before."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 426560.0,
      "end_time": 430880.0,
      "text": "We need to be open-minded. We need to be fluent."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 430880.0,
      "end_time": 435990.0,
      "text": "Look for alternatives, and not for the correct answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 435990.0,
      "end_time": 440160.0,
      "text": "Because when you think creatively, there&#39;s no single correct answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 440160.0,
      "end_time": 443852.0,
      "text": "There are many possible alternatives."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 443852.0,
      "end_time": 445480.0,
      "text": "Suppose now that we are lucky."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 445480.0,
      "end_time": 449320.0,
      "text": "We land upon a new idea in our travel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 449320.0,
      "end_time": 451990.0,
      "text": "in the exploration out of the box."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 451990.0,
      "end_time": 454120.0,
      "text": "What is the value of that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 454120.0,
      "end_time": 457240.0,
      "text": "How do we assess the value of a new idea?"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 457240.0,
      "end_time": 462000.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s very difficult if it&#39;s really new, because you&#39;ve never seen that before."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 462000.0,
      "end_time": 464600.0,
      "text": "Nobody else has seen that before."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 464600.0,
      "end_time": 471566.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s as if we landed on a new planet, totally undiscovered territory."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 471566.0,
      "end_time": 474800.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s difficult to understand the value of something new."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 474800.0,
      "end_time": 479040.0,
      "text": "First of all, because we don&#39;t feel entitled to be inventors."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 479040.0,
      "end_time": 482520.0,
      "text": "Who am I to be the generator of that new idea?"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 482520.0,
      "end_time": 485840.0,
      "text": "Probably this has been thought about before."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 485840.0,
      "end_time": 490000.0,
      "text": "If this is correct, somebody else would have done it before me."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 490000.0,
      "end_time": 495320.0,
      "text": "These are all natural mechanisms with which we kill our own ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 495320.0,
      "end_time": 497350.0,
      "text": "We have to resist that."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 497350.0,
      "end_time": 501600.0,
      "text": "We have to look for the match between the new idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 501600.0,
      "end_time": 504280.0,
      "text": "and our initial drive, our initial focus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 504280.0,
      "end_time": 509480.0,
      "text": "or evaluate the idea per se, for its own value"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 509480.0,
      "end_time": 513520.0,
      "text": "and maybe see that that&#39;s something that solves another problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 513520.0,
      "end_time": 515440.0,
      "text": "which it was not yours."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 515440.00000000006,
      "end_time": 518919.00000000006,
      "text": "Serendipity happens all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 518919.0,
      "end_time": 521840.0,
      "text": "We just need to have the eyes to see that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 521840.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525450.0,
      "text": "to notice the difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 525450.0,
      "end_time": 528080.0,
      "text": "Ok, but we are social animals."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 528080.0,
      "end_time": 529360.0,
      "text": "We live in an environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 529360.0,
      "end_time": 532040.0,
      "text": "so to think out of the box, bring in new ideas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 532040.0,
      "end_time": 534460.0,
      "text": "is going to challenge that environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 534460.0,
      "end_time": 539120.0,
      "text": "When is it a good idea to challenge everybody around you"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 539120.0,
      "end_time": 541210.0,
      "text": "in your working environment?"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 541210.0,
      "end_time": 542280.0,
      "text": "You have a boss."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 542280.0,
      "end_time": 545000.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t really want to upset him or her."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 545000.0,
      "end_time": 548280.0,
      "text": "When is it a good idea to think out of the box?"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 548280.0,
      "end_time": 553560.0,
      "text": "First of all, if the environment punishes mistakes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 553560.0,
      "end_time": 557320.0,
      "text": "you will never be really tempted to go out of the box."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 557320.0,
      "end_time": 561880.0,
      "text": "You will remain safely in a known environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 561880.0,
      "end_time": 565880.0,
      "text": "If you want to stimulate an environment which is creative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 565880.0,
      "end_time": 571200.0,
      "text": "you need to allow the existence of divergent information."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 571200.0,
      "end_time": 575080.0,
      "text": "You need to allow irrelevant information to come in."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 575080.0,
      "end_time": 578120.0,
      "text": "You have to mix and match different disciplines."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 578120.0,
      "end_time": 582200.0,
      "text": "You have to use metaphors in the organization."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 582200.0,
      "end_time": 586020.0,
      "text": "Only in that case, you will allow the environment"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 586020.0,
      "end_time": 591660.0,
      "text": "to be really prone to the generation of new ideas."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 591660.0,
      "end_time": 595080.0,
      "text": "I want to end my talk with a little experiment."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 595080.0,
      "end_time": 597160.0,
      "text": "We wanted to do this interactively with you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 597160.0,
      "end_time": 598800.0,
      "text": "but the time is scarce."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 598800.0,
      "end_time": 601600.0,
      "text": "I have indeed prepared a little thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 601600.0,
      "end_time": 604600.0,
      "text": "but if you believe me, and to be honest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 604600.0,
      "end_time": 607840.0,
      "text": "this has been generated in the space of few minutes."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 607840.0,
      "end_time": 611960.0,
      "text": "The generation of ideas, this travel outside of the box,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 611960.0,
      "end_time": 614240.0,
      "text": "is something which happens very fast."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 614240.0,
      "end_time": 616720.0,
      "text": "Where should we experiment?"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 616720.0,
      "end_time": 622360.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s say that we want to generate new ideas about TEDx Conferences."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 622360.0,
      "end_time": 627800.0,
      "text": "We are here, so that&#39;s a focused area which is very clear to all of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 627800.0,
      "end_time": 633600.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s start from the convergent information about TEDx Conferences."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 633600.0,
      "end_time": 638920.0,
      "text": "What is needed to make an excellent, good TEDx conference?"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 638920.0,
      "end_time": 642400.0,
      "text": "You need the brilliant speakers that will come up."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 642400.0,
      "end_time": 646660.0,
      "text": "You need an excellent theme."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 646660.0,
      "end_time": 651360.0,
      "text": "You need fast speaker to speaker transitions."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 651360.0,
      "end_time": 653880.0,
      "text": "You need grand settings."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 653880.0,
      "end_time": 660080.0,
      "text": "The list can go on, and all I&#39;m saying is things that you already know."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 660080.0,
      "end_time": 662960.0,
      "text": "This is all convergent information, safe."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 662960.0,
      "end_time": 666920.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not generating anything new. I&#39;m inside the box."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 666920.0,
      "end_time": 668920.0,
      "text": "Now I want to go out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 668920.0,
      "end_time": 672280.0,
      "text": "so I apply a divergent modifier"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 672280.0,
      "end_time": 675480.0,
      "text": "to any of these convergent elements."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 675480.0,
      "end_time": 679232.0,
      "text": "Start from the last one for example, the grand setting."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 679232.0,
      "end_time": 682520.0,
      "text": "A divergent modifier, for example, is to exaggerate."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 682520.0,
      "end_time": 684240.0,
      "text": "Bring it to the limit."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 684240.0,
      "end_time": 688600.0,
      "text": "Instead of thinking of a TEDx conferences in a theater,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 688600.0,
      "end_time": 692360.0,
      "text": "think of a TEDx Conference in a stadium."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 692360.0,
      "end_time": 694960.0,
      "text": "Does this make any sense, in a stadium?"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 694960.0,
      "end_time": 698280.0,
      "text": "Very difficult to organize, even more difficult than in a theater,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 698280.0,
      "end_time": 700920.0,
      "text": "and how do you fill the place?"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 700920.0,
      "end_time": 702400.0,
      "text": "How do you fill the stadium?"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 702400.0,
      "end_time": 705200.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s too difficult. It doesn&#39;t make any sense."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 705200.0,
      "end_time": 708040.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m tempted to reject that idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 708040.0,
      "end_time": 710760.0,
      "text": "But then I move, and I say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 710760.0,
      "end_time": 714880.0,
      "text": "ok, maybe the stadium is already filled with people."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 714880.0,
      "end_time": 717760.0,
      "text": "&gt;From that, you can get the idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 717760.0,
      "end_time": 723240.0,
      "text": "of having a TEDx Conference at half-time of football matches,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 723240.0,
      "end_time": 729840.0,
      "text": "a network of speeches which happens at half-time of football matches."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 729840.0,
      "end_time": 733600.0,
      "text": "Good idea, bad idea? I leave it for you to assess."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 733600.0,
      "end_time": 737320.0,
      "text": "Take another element: good speakers, brilliant speakers."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 737320.0,
      "end_time": 740760.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the most fundamental element of a TEDx Conference."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 740760.0,
      "end_time": 742240.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s take that away."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 742240.0,
      "end_time": 746590.0,
      "text": "We eliminate the good, brilliant speakers."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 746590.0,
      "end_time": 750720.0,
      "text": "Does this make any sense? No, we&#39;re out of the box."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 750720.0,
      "end_time": 753760.0,
      "text": "Does this lead to anything useful?"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 753760.0,
      "end_time": 757160.0,
      "text": "I could say that, OK, I don&#39;t need the speakers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 757160.0,
      "end_time": 761200.0,
      "text": "but I need the speeches, the talks, the scripts."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 761200.0,
      "end_time": 763280.0,
      "text": "&gt;From this comes the idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 763280.0,
      "end_time": 768400.0,
      "text": "of one speaker delivering the speech of somebody else."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 768400.0,
      "end_time": 770920.0,
      "text": "We exchange speakers."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 770920.0,
      "end_time": 774320.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s a cooperative TEDx Conference."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 774320.0,
      "end_time": 778000.0,
      "text": "Maybe we have duets on stage, instead of a single element,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 778000.0,
      "end_time": 782400.0,
      "text": "or we have people that speak about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 782400.0,
      "end_time": 783760.0,
      "text": "somebody has this topic."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 783760.0,
      "end_time": 786280.0,
      "text": "In that way we have one advantage at least."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 786280.0,
      "end_time": 788960.0,
      "text": "We take away the element of the ego."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 788960.0,
      "end_time": 790280.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s no ego anymore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 790280.0,
      "end_time": 793360.0,
      "text": "if you&#39;re speaking with somebody else&#39;s script."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 793360.0,
      "end_time": 796400.0,
      "text": "These are just examples, just examples,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 796400.0,
      "end_time": 800960.0,
      "text": "to show you that it&#39;s possible and not too hard, actually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 800960.0,
      "end_time": 802680.0,
      "text": "to think out of the box."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 802680.0,
      "end_time": 806440.0,
      "text": "I hope this journey, in a way, was interesting for you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 806440.0,
      "end_time": 809042.0,
      "text": "and now you want to do more of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 809042.0,
      "end_time": 811390.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much for your attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 811390.0,
      "end_time": 821390.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}